    'BEM naming: Block__Element--Modifier. Example: card__title--highlighted. Avoids class name conflicts.',
    'Media queries: @media (max-width: 768px) { } applies styles only on screens 768px wide or less.',
    'CSS specificity: inline style > id > class > element. Understanding this prevents style conflicts.',
    'CSS variables: --primary-color: #0D9488 defined in :root, used as color: var(--primary-color) everywhere.',
