    'I use it for: navbars, centering an element both vertically and horizontally, '
    'laying out a row of buttons or cards, and anywhere items need to flex and wrap. '
    'CSS Grid is two-dimensional — it handles rows AND columns simultaneously. '
    'I use it for: overall page layouts (header, sidebar, main, footer), '
